## How to Pin to Taskbar

Ikona **"Antigravity Workspace"** je registrovana u sistemu. Za pin:
- **GNOME**: Otvori Activities → traži "Antigravity" → desni klik → "Add to Favorites"
- **KDE**: Traži u Application Launcher → desni klik → "Pin to Task Manager"
- **XFCE**: Panel → Add New Items → Launcher → odaberi "Antigravity Workspace"

